query:
SELECT p.id, p.userId, p.company, p.deletedAt, COUNT(a.id) as assetCount
FROM projects p
LEFT JOIN assets a ON a.projectId = p.id
WHERE p.deletedAt IS NULL
GROUP BY p.id;
